1)react-fontawesome:-A React component for the font-awesome icon library.

https://www.npmjs.com/package/@fortawesome/react-fontawesome

ex:-
https://codesandbox.io/s/401k56m3kw?file=/src/styles.css:230-412

Installation
$ npm i --save @fortawesome/free-brands-svg-icons
$ npm i --save @fortawesome/fontawesome-svg-core
$ npm i --save @fortawesome/react-fontawesome

2)ReactPlayer:-A React component for playing a variety of URLs, including file paths, YouTube, Facebook,
 Twitch, SoundCloud, Streamable, Vimeo, Wistia, Mixcloud, and DailyMotion.
 
Usage:-
npm install react-player


3)react-share :- This library provides the most popular social media buttons. 
It is very easy to use and manage. It also supports various functionality like share, Like, follow.

Installation and Setup : npm install react-share 

https://medium.com/camperstribe/react-social-media-integration-with-react-share-and-react-helmet-84d9def6a445